title: De Guindos Says Catalonia Independence Won't Happen
description: Oct.05 -- Luis de Guindos, Spain’s economy minister, said Catalonian independence "is not going to take place" and that the enforcement of the law will be "perfectly implemented" by the government. He spoke with Bloomberg's Francine Lacqua on "Bloomberg Surveillance."
